01:09:29.995 --> 01:09:31.120
ALAN LIGHTMAN: [INAUDIBLE]?

01:09:31.120 --> 01:09:32.292
AUDIENCE: Sorry?

01:09:32.292 --> 01:09:34.470
ALAN LIGHTMAN: I didn't hear it.

01:09:34.470 --> 01:09:39.729
AUDIENCE: Like, your thoughts
around the existence of heaven

01:09:39.729 --> 01:09:41.500
or a hell type location.

01:09:41.500 --> 01:09:44.060
ALAN LIGHTMAN: Oh, well I don't
believe in heaven or hell.

01:09:44.060 --> 01:09:45.483
AUDIENCE: OK.

01:09:45.483 --> 01:09:46.149
Never mind then.

01:09:46.149 --> 01:09:47.274
ALAN LIGHTMAN: I mean, yes.

01:09:49.120 --> 01:09:50.470
I think this is it.

01:09:53.670 --> 01:09:56.365
Whatever we're experiencing
right now, this is it.

01:09:56.365 --> 01:09:59.266
And this is all there
is, in my opinion.

01:09:59.266 --> 01:10:01.640
But I don't know anything more
about this than any of you

01:10:01.640 --> 01:10:02.140
guys.

01:10:04.370 --> 01:10:05.830
Thank you very much.

